HEADWORD: Fumer
<hw>Fum"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One that
fumes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who makes or uses perfumes.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Embroiderers, feather makers, <qex>fumers</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Beau. & Fl.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fumerell</ent>⟦br⟧
